tinywm tiny window manager, 8l, public domain, 2016.

alt + left  : win move
alt + right : win resize
alt + a     : adjust 2 windows 
alt + f     : raise focused window
alt + tab   : toggle window and set focus
alt + r     : run dmenu             http://tools.suckless.org/dmenu/
alt + h     : show/hide window
alt + z     : zoom window
alt + x     : kill window
alt + esc   : exit tinywm

now focus problem gone, when start, just hit alt + tab.
close one term, then close all term.

